params.name: do_resize
params.description: Whether to resize the images (height, width) dimensions.

params.name: resample
params.description: Resampling filter to use when resizing the image.

params.name: do_rescale
params.description: Whether to rescale the image by the specified scale rescale_factor.

params.name: rescale_factor
params.description: Scale factor to use if rescaling the image.

params.name: image_mean
params.description: Mean to use if normalizing the image. This is a float or list of floats for each channel in the image.

params.name: image_std
params.description: Standard deviation to use if normalizing the image. This is a float or list of floats for each channel in the image.

params.name: do_convert_rgb
params.description: Whether to convert the image to RGB.

params.name: do_pad
params.description: Whether to pad the image. If True, will pad the patch dimension of the images in the batch to the largestnumber of patches in the batch. Padding will be applied to the bottom and right with zeros.

params.name: min_pixels
params.description: The min pixels of the image to resize the image.

params.name: max_pixels
params.description: The max pixels of the image to resize the image.

params.name: spatial_factor
params.description: The spatial downsample factor the image will be downsampled in feature extracting phase
